&lt;/div&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2013 12:04:23 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/tdf-resultados-preliminares-das-eleicoes-do-conselho-de-administracao</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/tdf-resultados-preliminares-das-eleicoes-do-conselho-de-administracao</guid></item><item><title>A TDF liberou LibreOffice 4.1.4</title><description>&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span title="This is the fifth release from the 4.1 branch of LibreOffice."&gt;A &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span title="This is the fifth release from the 4.1 branch of LibreOffice."&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span title="LibreOffice 4.1.4 Final (2013-12-18)"&gt;TDF liberou &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span title="This is the fifth release from the 4.1 branch of LibreOffice."&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span title="LibreOffice 4.1.4 Final (2013-12-18)"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span title="This is the fifth release from the 4.1 branch of LibreOffice."&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span title="LibreOffice 4.1.4 Final (2013-12-18)"&gt;hoje, dia 18 de dezembro de 2013, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;LibreOffice 4.1.4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, este é o quinto lançamento do ramo do LibreOffice 4.1.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;span title="It is the fourth bugfix release in the LibreOffice 4.1.x line which contains many exciting new features, and is suitable for all users — for conservative requirements, we refer you to LibreOffice 4.0.6 from the previous series."&gt;É a quarta versão de correções do LibreOffice 4.1.x.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img src="/articles/0132/0221/nova-versao.png" height="273" alt="" width="442"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;span title="It is the fourth bugfix release in the LibreOffice 4.1.x line which contains many exciting new features, and is suitable for all users — for conservative requirements, we refer you to LibreOffice 4.0.6 from the previous series."&gt;Conheça os novos recursos da versão LibreOffice 4.1, &lt;a href="http://pt-br.libreoffice.org/index.php/baixe-ja/novos-recursos/libreoffice-4-1/" target="_blank"&gt;aqui!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;O LibreOffice é uma suite de escritório livre compatível com as principais suítes de escritório do mercado. Oferece todas as funções esperadas de uma suite profissional: editor de textos, planilha, apresentação, editor de desenhos e banco de dados.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;span title="It is the fourth bugfix release in the LibreOffice 4.1.x line which contains many exciting new features, and is suitable for all users — for conservative requirements, we refer you to LibreOffice 4.0.6 from the previous series."&gt;Para download, acesse &lt;a href="http://pt-br.libreoffice.org/index.php/baixe-ja" target="_blank"&gt;aqui!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span title="It is the fourth bugfix release in the LibreOffice 4.1.x line which contains many exciting new features, and is suitable for all users — for conservative requirements, we refer you to LibreOffice 4.0.6 from the previous series."&gt;http://pt-br.libreoffice.org/index.php/baixe-ja/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span title="It is the fourth bugfix release in the LibreOffice 4.1.x line which contains many exciting new features, and is suitable for all users — for conservative requirements, we refer you to LibreOffice 4.0.6 from the previous series."&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;por Vitorio Furusho&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span title="It is the fourth bugfix release in the LibreOffice 4.1.x line which contains many exciting new features, and is suitable for all users — for conservative requirements, we refer you to LibreOffice 4.0.6 from the previous series."&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2013 10:33:19 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/a-tdf-liberou-libreoffice-4.1.4</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/a-tdf-liberou-libreoffice-4.1.4</guid></item><item><title>TDF liberou o LibreOffice 4.2 beta 2 para testes.</title><description>&lt;h5 class="uiStreamMessage userContentWrapper"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;span class="messageBody"&gt;&lt;span class="userContent" style="font-family: inherit; font-size: small;"&gt;TDF liberou o LibreOffice 4.2 beta 2 para testes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;h5 class="uiStreamMessage userContentWrapper"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;span class="messageBody"&gt;&lt;span class="userContent" style="font-family: inherit; font-size: small;"&gt;Eis algumas das novidades:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;h5 class="uiStreamMessage userContentWrapper"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;span class="messageBody"&gt;&lt;span class="userContent" style="font-family: inherit; font-size: small;"&gt;* Muito mais rápido&lt;br&gt; * Novo StartCenter&lt;br&gt;* Menu de aplicativos no Lançador LibreOffice (Ubuntu)&lt;br&gt; * Importa arquivos do Visio&lt;br&gt; * Importa arquivos do Publisher&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p class="separator" style="text-align: center; clear: both;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-crZZ0bScgkY/UqJH3pDzdaI/AAAAAAAAAG4/FBkbJu_MugE/s1600/Pre-Lancamento.png" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-crZZ0bScgkY/UqJH3pDzdaI/AAAAAAAAAG4/FBkbJu_MugE/s400/Pre-Lancamento.png" border="0" height="226" alt="" width="400"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5 class="uiStreamMessage userContentWrapper" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: normal;"&gt;No Ubuntu: Uma novidade interessante, você não precisa instalar um lançador pra cada programa do LibreOffice, adicione apenas o lançador principal do LibreOffice. Para ativar um dos programas, basta clicar com botão direito do mouse no lançador LibreOffice e a opção desejada. veja a segunda imagem.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;h5 class="uiStreamMessage userContentWrapper" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: normal;"&gt;Gostaríamos de lembrá-los que esse release deve ser usado somente para testes. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
